  "prompt": "Which is the best phone under 16k INR?",
  "response": "As of October 2023, there are several excellent smartphones available under **16,000 INR** that offer great value for money. Here\u2019s a list of some of the best options based on performance, camera quality, battery life, and overall features:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Redmi Note 12 4G**\n- **Key Features**: 6.67-inch AMOLED display, 50MP triple camera, Snapdragon 685 processor, 5000mAh battery, 33W fast charging.\n- **Why Buy**: Great display, decent performance, and excellent battery life.\n\n---\n\n### **2. Realme Narzo 60x 5G**\n- **Key Features**: 6.72-inch FHD+ display, 50MP dual camera, Dimensity 6100+ processor, 5000mAh battery, 33W fast charging.\n- **Why Buy**: Affordable 5G phone with good performance and a sleek design.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Samsung Galaxy M14 5G**\n- **Key Features**: 6.6-inch FHD+ display, 50MP triple camera, Exynos 1330 processor, 6000mAh battery, 25W fast charging.\n- **Why Buy**: Long-lasting battery and 5G support at an affordable price.\n\n---\n\n### **4. Poco M6 Pro 5G**\n- **Key Features**: 6.79-inch FHD+ display, 50MP dual camera, Snapdragon 4 Gen 1 processor, 5000mAh battery, 18W fast charging.\n- **Why Buy**: Solid performance and 5G capability in an affordable package.\n\n---\n\n### **5. Infinix Zero 30 4G**\n- **Key Features**: 6.78-inch AMOLED display, 108MP main camera, Helio G99 processor, 5000mAh battery, 68W fast charging.\n- **Why Buy**: Premium AMOLED display and fast charging at a budget price.\n\n---\n\n### **6. Tecno Pova 5**\n- **Key Features**: 6.78-inch FHD+ display, 50MP dual camera, Helio G99 processor, 6000mAh battery, 45W fast charging.\n- **Why Buy**: Massive battery and fast charging for heavy users.\n\n---\n\n### **7. Motorola G54 5G**\n- **Key Features**: 6.5-inch FHD+ display, 50MP dual camera, Dimensity 7020 processor, 5000mAh battery, 15W charging.\n- **Why Buy**: Clean Android experience and reliable performance.\n\n---\n\n### **Factors to Consider When Choosing:**\n1. **Processor**: Look for Snapdragon 600/700 series or MediaTek Dimensity series for smooth performance.\n2. **Display**: AMOLED is better for vibrant colors, but FHD+ LCD is also good.\n3. **Battery**: 5000mAh or higher is ideal for long-lasting usage.\n4. **Camera**: Higher megapixels (50MP+) and additional lenses improve photography.\n5. **5G Support**: Future-proof your purchase with a 5G-enabled phone.\n\n---\n\n**Best Overall**: **Redmi Note 12 4G** (for AMOLED display and balanced performance).  \n**Best for 5G**: **Realme Narzo 60x 5G** or **Poco M6 Pro 5G**.\n\nMake sure to check for the latest offers and discounts before purchasing!",
